title: Tin Foil Hat #53: Mysterious Celebrity Deaths with Ron Placone
description:
Thanks for listening to another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. On this episode, Ryan and Sam welcome comedian Ron Placone. On this episode we discuss...
1) The Jimmy Dore Show
2)Net Neutrality
3) RT News
4) Marylin Monroe, The Kennedys and UFOs
5) Bob Marley, The CIA and Nazis
5) Kurt Cobain
Please check out our Patreon Channel for premium content of the podcast, Patreon.com/TinFoilHat!
Thank you for your support!
